data.description: This house is AMAZING!! Totally remodeled in Shorewood/Joliet's sought after Camelot Subdivision with Minooka schools! Prepare to be wowed as soon as you walk in and see the soaring two-sided 2 story fireplace, dramatic staircase, and wide open layout. This beautiful home offers hardwood flooring throughout the first and second floor. 3 first floor bedrooms with 1.5 baths on first level, and 2nd floor master with an incredible remodeled bath. This home can live like a ranch property - choose one of 2 master bedrooms. 1 on main floor or stunning master suite on 2 level featuring huge closet and private luxury bathroom with walk in shower, and dual vanity! Beautiful remodeled kitchen opens to family room and offers brand new stainless steel appliances, level 5 quartz countertops, and two-tone cabinetry. Massive family room is perfect for entertaining all your guests. First floor full bath offers amazing shower with brass fixtures and tile surround, LED bathroom mirror, and brand new vanity. First floor laundry with barnwood surround, and remodeled half bath. Full finished basement with brand new vinyl plank flooring, and 3rd full bathroom! This house is loaded with sunlight and is a refreshing break from the cookie cutter homes in surrounding neighborhoods. Exterior features newer vinyl siding, large deck, and private HALF ACRE lot that backs to wooded area. Brand new furnace 2023. Brand new water heater 2023. Gutter Guards, roof is less than 10 years old + Andersen windows! This is one special property. Get in ASAP before it's gone.
